Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph queue target

Purpose:
  Change the task of an existing active job.

Usage:
  wikigraph queue target <job-id> --task <reading-graph|reading-summary|knowledge-graph>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Options:
  --task <task>         New task.

Example:
  wikigraph queue target 75d12f7e --task reading-summary
